---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro"
import Testimonials from "../components/Testimonials.astro"
import CTA from "../components/CTA.astro"

const title = "Mobile Tyre Fitting In Nottingham"
const description = "Change your tyres at home with our mobile tyre fitting service. We cover Nottingham and surrounding areas. Call us today for a quote."
const index = true
const bgImg = "url('/img/mobile-tyre-fitting-van.jpg')"
const heading = "The Easy Way to Change Your Tyres"
const tagline = "Have your tyres fitted at home or work"
const formOption = "tyreclick"
const mainHeading = "Mobile Tyre Fitting In Nottingham"
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} index={index}>
    <Hero heading={heading} tagline={tagline} bgImg={bgImg} formOption={formOption} />
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="row">
            <main class="col-12 col-lg-8">
                <h1 class="text-center text-lg-start">{mainHeading}</h1>
                <p><strong>Mobile tyre fitting</strong> is a relatively new but rapidly expanding industry due to the convenience of the service that is offered.</p>
                <p>You simply call us with the <strong>tyre size</strong> of your vehicle and we can be at your location within <em>90 minutes</em> to replace your tyres. This can either be done as an <a href="/emergency-tyre-replacement">emergency in a breakdown situation</a> or as a replacement service to using your local garage.</p>
                <p>Modern technology has allowed for this service to come at no extra cost.</p>
                <p>All of our vans have been equipped with the best equipment money can buy and is suitable to use with all tyres, including <a href="/posts/what-is-a-run-flat-tyre">run flats</a> and low profile tyres.</p>
                <p>We can also replace tyres that have Tyron bands fitted such as <a href="/mobile-caravan-tyre-fitting">caravan tyres.</a></p>
                <h2>Mobile Tyre Fitting Covering the Whole of Nottingham</h2>
                <p>With multiple vans in <strong>Nottingham</strong>, we aim to respond to any <strong>tyre call-outs</strong> within 90 minutes.</p>
                <p>We cover Arnold, Beeston, Carlton, Hucknall, Ilkeston, Kirkby-In-Ashfield, Long Eaton, Mansfield, Newark, Sutton-In-Ashfield, West Bridgford, Worksop and surrounding areas.</p>
            </main>
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
                <aside class="container">
                    <div class="border rounded-3 shadow-sm py-4 row mb-3">
                        <div class="col-3 text-center">
                            <i class="bi bi-calendar fs-1"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9 text-start">
                            <h3 class="mb-0">Flexible Service</h3>
                            <p class="mb-0">Open 6 days a week</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border rounded-3 shadow-sm py-4 bg-dark text-white row mb-3">
                        <div class="col-3 text-center">
                            <i class="bi bi-car-front fs-1"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9 text-start">
                            <h3 class="mb-0">Fast Arrival</h3>
                            <p class="mb-0">Same day service</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border rounded-3 shadow-sm bg-success text-white py-4 row mb-3">
                        <div class="col-3 text-center">
                            <i class="bi bi-map fs-1"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9 text-start">
                            <h3 class="mb-0">Local Areas</h3>
                            <p class="mb-0">We serve {title} and surrounding areas</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </aside>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <Testimonials />
    <CTA />
</Layout>